A light-weight sentence tokenizer for Japanese.


Sample Code:

from ja_sentence.tokenizer import tokenize

paragraph_str = "えー！？くれるの？本当にいいの…？嬉しい！！"

sentence_list = tokenize(paragraph_str)

for sentence in sentence_list:
	print(sentence)


